30px\"><p>強勢股分享</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>【上櫃量大上漲股】</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4991:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4991\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4991-TW</a>) 環宇 - KY</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3508:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3508\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3508-TW</a>) 位速</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6640:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6640\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6640-TW</a>) 均華</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4979:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4979\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4979-TW</a>) 星光</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4549:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4549\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4549-TW</a>) 桓達</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6596:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6596\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6596-TW</a>) 寬宏藝術</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4971:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4971\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4971-TW</a>)IET-KY</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWG:6584:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6584\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6584-TW</a>) 南俊國際</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6274:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6274\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6274-TW</a>) 台燿</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6234:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6234\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6234-TW</a>) 高僑</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><figure><img src=\"https://cimg.cnyes.cool/prod/news/6050909/l/5f907ddd0c0c36a48f903ea3de992bc0.jpg\"/></figure></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>想持股診斷或詢問盤勢分析<br/>\n請免費訂閱<br/>\n股市期皇后 莊佳螢</p></section><section style=\"m